vb.stil.codegenerator

Class CodeGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • vb.stil.codegenerator.CodeGenerator

  • public class CodeGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Parses the decorated AST and generates code by utilising StringTemplates. This is mostly done by passing the root node, the program then intelligently determines the structure of the child nodes.
    Version:
    7-7-2014
    Author:
    Bas Veeling, Jarno van Leeuwen
